sequenceDiagram
    participant M as Master
    participant D as Dashboard
    participant PS as Practice Service
    participant Z as Zoom API
    participant DB as Database

    M->>D: Create new practice
    D->>PS: POST /api/v1/practices
    PS->>Z: POST /users/me/meetings
    Note over Z: Create scheduled meeting
    Z-->>PS: meeting_id, join_url, host_url, password
    PS->>DB: Save practice with Zoom data
    DB-->>PS: practice_id
    PS-->>D: Practice created
    D-->>M: Success + preview
    
    Note over M,Z: Before practice starts
    
    M->>D: Click Start Practice
    D->>PS: GET /api/v1/practices/id/host-url
    PS-->>D: host_url
    D->>M: Open Zoom as host
